title: Al-juzʼ al-awwal min kitāb Mashāriq al-anwār al-Qudsīyah fī bayān al-ʻuhūd al-Muḥammadīyah al-shahīr bi-al-ʻUhūd al-kubrá.|الجزء الاول من كتاب مشارق الانوار القدسية في بيان العهود المحمدية الشهير بالعهود الكبرى
additional_titles: Al-juzʼ al-awwal min kitāb Mashāriq al-anwār al-Qudsīyah fī bayān al-ʻuhūd al-Muḥammadīyah al-shahīr bi-al-ʻUhūd al-kubrá
authors: Shaʻrānī, ʻAbd al-Wahhāb ibn Aḥmad, approximately 1493-1565 or 1566
